domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div><h3>读这个：</h3><p>并非 Engadget 上的所有内容都受益于大量的释义和一个人对着镜头说话不到 10 分钟。本周，我们来看看 OpenAI 聊天机器人 ChatGPT 的成长、成长和进一步成长的<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/how-openais-chatgpt-has-changed-the-world-in-just-a-year-140050053.html">精彩简介</a>。它为更广泛的公众重新构建了生成式人工智能，并让最大的科技公司竞相追赶。那只是它的第一年。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p><em>比起视频更喜欢电子邮件？</em><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/about/newsletter/"><em>在这里订阅</em></a><em>每日报告，直接发送到您的收件箱。</em></p><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-googles-geo Thermal-power-plant-in-the-desert-and-more-140010085.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-googles-geothermal-power-plant-in-the-desert-and-more-140010085.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> cd4e3dea-e4d6-46dd-ab51-03a710901fcd</guid><dc:creator>马特·史密斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 14:00:10 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1701469016</ingested><modified> 2023-12-01T22:16:58+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mat Smith]]></category><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F7e271a10-9096-11ee-bbf7-c4ccf29b654f&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=fe359b81798acedd232a79ec9165d25e2d2d7916" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDAT